    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build words, play cards, and take flight!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A deckbuilding word game inspired by <i>Wordle</i>, <i>Scrabble</i> and <i>Balatro</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize, build your deck and build up your high score</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide your adorable flock on a round-the-world migration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roguelike elements – how far will your flock go? </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264170/extras/18dc6cf605cfb51d0aaab670b0d49950.poster.avif?t=1754362824\" width=800 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264170/extras/18dc6cf605cfb51d0aaab670b0d49950.webm?t=1754362824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264170/extras/18dc6cf605cfb51d0aaab670b0d49950.mp4?t=1754362824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Birdigo is an adorable mashup of <i>Wordle</i> and <i>Balatro</i> created by screenwriter John August (<i>Corpse Bride, Charlie’s Angels</i>) and developer Corey Martin (<i>Bonfire Peaks, Pipe Push Paradise</i>). Piece together words from your deck of letters and guide a flock of birds in their migration around the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264170/extras/7e88dd5bfdf64479d63e1272739eafe8.poster.avif?t=1754362824\" width=700 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264170/extras/7e88dd5bfdf64479d63e1272739eafe8.webm?t=1754362824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264170/extras/7e88dd5bfdf64479d63e1272739eafe8.mp4?t=1754362824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble letter cards into words, which add up into ‘flaps’ to send you further along your journey. Longer words score higher, but specific combos can turn short words into powerhouses. Use enchanted feathers, letters and songs to change the rules of the game as you go.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build up your deck and develop your own strategy in each game. You’ll need to play carefully, as the distance gets further with each round. Stack up a massive high score and guide your flock to safety!  <br>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2>",
